#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This page has instructions directly on it - just drag around the buttons "
#| "until you have the order that makes you comfortable."
msgid ""
"This page allows you to customize the button location on the titlebar. You "
"can drag buttons &eg; the <guilabel>Application menu</guilabel> into the "
"titlebar, remove them or drag around the buttons until you have the order "
"that makes you comfortable."
msgstr ""
"このページの操作方法は直接的なものです。 - お好きな順になるようにボタンをド"
"ラッグして並べ替えて下さい。"

